tip.text: Buttermilk fish-must try, an alternative to chicken. 😋
Yam basket is fresh and delicious.
Nasi lemak yummy and order an extra side of fried chicken wing crunchy and tasty!
New special of the day, Lamb Stew is tasty. You can choose if you want it with rice or pasta.
Carrot cake taste fresh. Had the tuna sandwich the bread was good.
